A) How to create a repository
Go to homepage,click NEW option,and now enter details of repository.

B)How  to create a file
Homepage >Your Repo >Add file

C)How to create a branch
Homepage >Your Repo 
Click on the dropdown menu which appears on left.It shows branch name.
Click it and now enter your branch name.

D)How to add collaborator
Settings> Collaborators 
Click on the add people option in the right.
(The access of collaborators is limited to the repo to which you add them)

E)How to update a file
HomePage>Your repo > code
click on the file name you want to edit
Click on the edit option in the right

F)How to create a pull request
Homepage>Your Repo >Pull Request


E)How to request a review from collaborator
Step 1: Add collaborator
Step 2: Request review
Your repo > Pull request >Click on reviewer on the right.

G)How to merge changes after approval

H)How to check if changes have been approved






